[- See Torsten Brinch's post archive.960606 "BSE & TME (3)" for a discussion
on the relationships of this disease with scrapie and TME. It appears to be
not scrapie but whether it is related to TME or the Cow-adapted TME is unknown.
Whether it is epidemiologically important that some of these affected deer
were being kept in captivity is also unclear. MHJ]
